Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Laoac Central School in the Municipality of Laoac, Province of Pangasinan, to Don Rufino Tabayoyong Central School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 770
An Act Changing the Name of the Laoac Central School in the Municipality of Laoac, Province of Pangasinan, to Don Rufino Tabayoyong Central School
Section 1. The name of the Laoac Central School in the Municipality of Laoac, Province of Pangasinan, is changed to Don Rufino Tabayoyong Central School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
